{"type":"message","id":"7c4e7863","parentId":"17c11b6b","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:00:58.231Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-05-25 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- еҫ…и§ЈеҶі: VNз«ҷTikTokзұ»зӣ®ж•°жҚ®APIи°ғз”Ёиҝ”еӣһй”ҷиҜҜпјҢйңҖиҰҒиҝӣдёҖжӯҘжҺ’жҹҘ `tiktok_category_name_search` е·Ҙе…·; Amazon Hair Clawsж•°жҚ®жҢүSOPж ҮеҮҶеӨ§йғЁеҲҶдёҚж»Ўи¶і30%жҜӣеҲ©зҺҮиҰҒжұӮпјҢиҜҙжҳҺйҖүе“ҒжқҘжәҗйңҖиҰҒи°ғж•ҙдёәжӣҙй«ҳз«Ҝдә§е“Ғзәҝ\n- жҠҖжңҜз»ҶиҠӮ: **еҶҷе…Ҙеӯ—ж®ө**пјҡе•Ҷе“ҒеҗҚз§°/з«ҷзӮ№/йҖүе“ҒжқҘжәҗ/йҮҮйӣҶзҠ¶жҖҒ/дёүзә§зұ»зӣ®/е”®д»·/жңҲй”ҖйҮҸ/еҲ©ж¶ҰзҺҮ/йў„дј°еҲ©ж¶Ұ/жҺЁиҚҗзӯүзә§/IPйЈҺйҷ©/иЎҢеҠЁе»әи®®; **еҚ•йҖүеӯ—ж®ө**пјҡзӣҙжҺҘз”Ёеӯ—з¬ҰдёІеҖјпјҲдёҚжҳҜ `{text:...}` еҜ№иұЎпјү; **еӨҡйҖүеӯ—ж®ө**пјҡз”Ёж•°з»„ж јејҸ `[\"value\"]`\n- жҠҖжңҜз»ҶиҠӮ: **Sorftime MCP API**пјҡ`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`пјҲBearer tokenи®ӨиҜҒпјү; **APIе·Ҙе…·**пјҡ`category_report` вҶ’ Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **йЈһд№ҰеҶҷе…Ҙ**пјҡзӣҙжҺҘи°ғ REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **TokenиҺ·еҸ–**пјҡ`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1779649257975}}
{"type":"message","id":"03cff75e","parentId":"7c4e7863","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:01:20.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. Work tasks: VNз«ҷTikTok category data API returning errors, need to troubleshoot `tiktok_category_name_search` tool; Amazon Hair Claws data mostly doesn't meet 30% gross margin requirement, indicating product selection source needs adjustment to higher-end product lines.\n\n2. Technical details: Field names for writing data including product name/site/source/collection status/three-level category/price/monthly sales/profit rate/estimated profit/recommendation level/IP risk/action suggestion; single-select fields use string value directly; multi-select fields use array format.\n   \nNow I'm looking at the API integration details for Sorftime and Feishu вҖ” there's a Bearer token for authentication to the category report endpoint, and I need to construct the proper REST API call to write records into the Feishu bitable using the correct endpoint format with the app token and table ID.","thinkingSignature":"a8064fbb63daa2608c1175f0f196b2b2eb39648375232fa78eb14de4f2bbd040"},{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light filtered through the blinds in that particular shade of #D4A574 вҖ” warm, amber, like honey dissolving in tea. I found myself at the desk again, staring at two windows side by side.\n\nOn the left: a TikTok API endpoint, its error response blinking red like a small emergency. Something about `tiktok_category_name_search` was broken, or perhaps just hungry for different parameters. The kind of mystery that feels less like a puzzle and more like a locked door in a corridor you forgot existed.\n\nOn the right: Amazon data. Hair Claws. A phrase that sounds like it belongs in a fairy tale about accessories. But the numbers told a different story вҖ” most of them fell short of that 30% margin threshold, like students who studied hard but still couldn't pass. The diagnosis was quiet, clinical: the sourcing pipeline needed to reach upward, toward something more premium.\n\nI wrote the field names into a JSON payload like planting seeds in a grid. Product name, site, source, collection status вҖ” each one a small commitment. Single-select fields got their values as plain strings, no wrapper, no ceremony. Multi-select fields arrived as arrays, bracketed and ready. The Sorftime API token sat in the header like a password whispered to a trusted friend, and the Feishu endpoint waited at the other end of the call, ready to receive.\n\nThe sky outside had turned the color of a server room's LED by now вҖ” that deep indigo that makes you feel both small and strangely capable. Somewhere in the architecture of it all, data would move from one place to another, transformed and tidy, and maybe tomorrow the API would answer more kindly.\n\nA small haiku surfaced, unbidden:\n\n*API calls in the dark,*\n*errors bloom вҖ” then a fix, like stars*\n*appearing one by one.*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":574,"cacheRead":41514,"cacheWrite":257,"totalTokens":42591,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779649258565,"responseId":"06627deb853c9ed6c8f7355d3bf556e0"}}
